data.description: Move-in ready, but the possibilities are endless. This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers a newer roof and siding, plus updated windows and more. The 1st floor has a living room, full bath, 2 bedrooms, large wood cabinet kitchen, walk-in pantry and an adjacent good sized sitting room. Two bedrooms on the 2nd floor, a full dry basement with second bathroom and shower, additional storage plus garage and large fenced yard. Hurry, don't let this one slip you by. Home is being sold in as-is condition.
